title: Rishi Sunak calls on G7 Finance Ministers and Central Bank Governors to go faster and further in support of Ukraine - GOV.UK
content: Rishi Sunak calls on G7 Finance Ministers and Central Bank Governors to go faster and further in support of Ukraine  GOV.UK
description: During the first meeting of G7 Finance Ministers and Central Bank Governors under the German Presidency, Rishi Sunak called on the group to go “faster and further” in support of Ukraine.
